6:
I want to become a Champion
princess!
10:
Hmm, is that so? Unfortunately, one
doesn't simply become a Champion
by wishing upon it—no matter how
fervently.
12:
Besides. You may be undead, but I
would still be remiss about taking a
young girl such as you onto the
battlefield.
17:
Light, I don't think that's what she
had in mind.
20:
Fine, I can call it something else. I
want to be... a magical princess!
25:
Just what exactly is that supposed
to mean?
28:
She wishes for you to accompany
her on her day off.
31:
This Saga has all sorts of magic and
weird stuff going on, right?
33:
It's just like one of my Japanese
animes! I can go around and beat
up some monsters or something!
38:
Oh I get it, you want to follow us
around and play hero, huh?
42:
Unfortunately, we are not familiar
with the locale. It would be most
helpful if we could call upon you for
help, Alk.
46:
I see. I can do that no problem, I
happen to be free today!
51:
Really?! Awesome! Thank you so
much!
54:
Okay, take me somewhere with tons
of monsters. I'm gonna let them
have it!
64:
Just you wait, world! Lily's coming to
protect you! Hyah!
68:
Wow, wow! It's like I'm using real
magic!
71:
I guess it does look like magic, huh?
It's really all thanks to the various
weapons and tools we have at our
disposal!
79:
If this is the extent of our plans for
today, I imagine there won't be any
problems.
84:
Yep. Oh, I also made lunch for us.
Are you feeling hungry?
87:
Oh, you made special bento boxes
for us, Alk? Awesome!
92:
Yeah, I made a few sandwiches
and—huh?
95:
Oh no, I forgot to pack them! Sorry
guys, I'll go back and grab them, just
wait for me here!
107: I'm not a pipsqueak! I'm Lily!
110:
All right, Lily. Do you really get a kick
out of just beatin' up monsters?
113: Yes! It's super fun! And MAGICAL!
115:
Shouldn't a kid like you be off
playing hide or seek instead? Not
sure idols are cut out for fightin' like
this.
120:
Huh? We are too! I can look after
myself, you know!
123:
Mhm. Just remember that it's not all
sunshine and roses. When push
comes to shove, you might have to
defend yourself.
127:
I know that! I'm Lily Hoshikawa, I'm
not going to let a monster
jeopardize my idol career!
133:
Sorry for the wait! I'll get lunch ready
right away.
137:
I'm starving! I can't wait to eat what
you've got for us!
140: And here we go, help yourselves!
146:
I don't think I've EVER eaten bread
this soft before!
150:
See, I knew you'd like it! Alk's cooking
really is incredible!
155:
We're really singin' Alk's praises
today, huh?
163:
Hey, you! Do you want to eat lunch
with us?
166: Oh, he left. I wonder why.
171:
I've never seen an outfit like that...
Maybe he's a drifter?
175: A drifter? What do you mean?
180:
Oh, so he was from another world?
Just like me.
181: And he's probably all on his own...
184:
Probably. That'd explain why he was
all sneaky and on high alert.
188:
I... I'm going to go after him! I'll be
back soon.
200:
You were... watching us eat back
there, right? Is something wrong?
203:
I'm Number 6! Oh, that means I'm an
idol from Saga.
208:
That's right, from a dazzling group
called Franchouchou!
211:
If you're ever in Saga, please come
to our concert! Okay, see you later!
